snippet.title: Jesse Eckel
snippet.description:
I’m on a journey to make a million dollars in a year from brand new businesses I just started. I talk about business, investing, finances, mindset, marketing, crypto investing and more.

I’m an entrepreneur, dad, and creative. Follow along for the journey!🥳
